data.description: This two-bedroom, two full bathroom ranch-style condominium offers the perfect trifecta: great space, great layout & great location. A welcoming foyer with guest coat closet flows seamlessly into the open concept living room/dining room, allowing great space for entertaining family & friends. The kitchen offers generous space for both cooking & dining. An en-suite primary bedroom features a sitting area, walk-in closet & access to a private balcony, perfect for enjoying morning coffee under the sun or a glass of wine under the stars. A second bedroom offers a full wall of generous closet space. Association amenities include a Clubhouse, Fitness Room, Heated Outdoor Pool, Additional Storage & Professional On-Site Management. There is assigned parking for 1 car as well as additional parking for visitors. The HOA fee includes all but electric, phone & cable. Welcome home to easy living in Vinnin Square where all your needs...transportation, shops & restaurants...are just steps away!
